WEBVTT

00:00:00.140 --> 00:00:03.060
=The Crow Princess of Fortune=

00:00:03.060 --> 00:00:04.980
=Episode 13=

00:00:06.820 --> 00:00:07.739
What are you doing?

00:00:07.740 --> 00:00:09.940
Money you give me stays mine.

00:00:11.460 --> 00:00:13.780
Are you too broke to eat now?

00:00:16.420 --> 00:00:17.540
Here, take this.

00:00:19.820 --> 00:00:21.300
Let's go.

00:00:26.900 --> 00:00:28.939
Your Highness,
are we still going after her?

00:00:28.940 --> 00:00:30.459
Going after her for what?

00:00:30.460 --> 00:00:32.899
From now on, whoever dares bully Suisui

00:00:32.900 --> 00:00:35.460
is making an enemy of me.

00:00:37.300 --> 00:00:40.380
Later, hand all
the protection fees over to her.

00:00:43.320 --> 00:00:46.480
(Imperial Academy)

00:00:48.820 --> 00:00:49.659
Your Highness.

00:00:49.660 --> 00:00:51.739
You've been standing here
for half an hour already.

00:00:51.740 --> 00:00:54.020
- Why don't you sit down for a while?
- No.

00:00:54.140 --> 00:00:56.620
Your leg just recovered,
and you've been standing this long.

00:00:56.780 --> 00:00:57.439
Come on.

00:00:57.440 --> 00:00:58.550
Dajun.

00:00:58.640 --> 00:01:01.419
Look what time it is already.

00:01:01.420 --> 00:01:03.299
Why isn't the Little Princess out yet?

00:01:03.300 --> 00:01:05.540
How could His Highness not be worried?

00:01:07.740 --> 00:01:09.619
Oh, right.

00:01:09.620 --> 00:01:13.580
Do you think our Little Princess might
be getting bullied by her classmates?

00:01:13.660 --> 00:01:15.459
Shi, you're overthinking it.

00:01:15.460 --> 00:01:16.479
It's already good enough

00:01:16.480 --> 00:01:18.140
if our Little Princess
doesn't bully others.

00:01:18.740 --> 00:01:20.860
You think
the Little Princess bullies people?

00:01:22.780 --> 00:01:24.460
Now that I think about it, maybe.

00:01:25.260 --> 00:01:28.379
No, wait.
The Little Princess loves money so much.

00:01:28.380 --> 00:01:31.379
If she bullied someone, she'd definitely
squeeze some silver out of them.

00:01:31.380 --> 00:01:34.019
But what if she gets too much silver
and can't carry it all?

00:01:34.020 --> 00:01:35.700
No, this won't do.

00:01:35.820 --> 00:01:37.219
The courtyard wall isn't that high.

00:01:37.220 --> 00:01:39.740
You're good at this stuff.
Climb in and see if she needs help.

00:01:39.860 --> 00:01:41.579
What silver? Why should I climb in?

00:01:41.580 --> 00:01:43.139
Look at you. Useless when it matters.

00:01:43.140 --> 00:01:44.139
Are you going or not?

00:01:44.140 --> 00:01:45.380
If you won't go, I will.

00:01:46.460 --> 00:01:47.900
Suisui.

00:01:48.020 --> 00:01:49.460
Little Princess.

00:01:49.500 --> 00:01:52.820
Father, I really loves going to school.

00:01:58.060 --> 00:02:01.339
Prince Jing,
ever since Suisui entered the palace,

00:02:01.340 --> 00:02:03.099
your health has fully recovered.

00:02:03.100 --> 00:02:04.740
Your mood has improved quite a bit too.

00:02:05.660 --> 00:02:07.500
I know you cherish this child,

00:02:07.700 --> 00:02:10.899
but everything has its limits.

00:02:10.900 --> 00:02:14.180
I've heard she turned
the Imperial Academy upside down

00:02:14.220 --> 00:02:15.860
and even started doing business there.

00:02:15.900 --> 00:02:19.140
Suisui does have a talent for business.

00:02:20.580 --> 00:02:22.580
Was I praising you?

00:02:22.660 --> 00:02:26.100
I was reminding you
not to spoil her too much.

00:02:26.620 --> 00:02:28.619
Suisui is Heaven's blessed lucky star.

00:02:28.620 --> 00:02:30.420
Father will understand in time.

00:02:40.500 --> 00:02:41.899
Suisui.

00:02:41.900 --> 00:02:43.780
What are you looking for?

00:02:44.700 --> 00:02:45.739
Grandfather.

00:02:45.740 --> 00:02:48.620
Why does your room feel so strange?

00:02:50.060 --> 00:02:52.939
Dust on the beams,
empty under the eaves.

00:02:52.940 --> 00:02:55.780
A hole by the wall leads underground.

00:02:55.900 --> 00:02:58.459
Treasure lies beneath the Dragon Throne.

00:02:58.460 --> 00:03:01.420
Too bad Grandfather
can't sit steady on it.

00:03:01.980 --> 00:03:03.420
How dare you!

00:03:04.020 --> 00:03:05.180
Father, please calm down.

00:03:05.260 --> 00:03:06.619
Suisui is still young

00:03:06.620 --> 00:03:07.780
and spoke carelessly.

00:03:07.780 --> 00:03:09.400
I am willing to take
the punishment for her.

00:03:09.860 --> 00:03:12.179
Grandfather, don't be angry.

00:03:12.180 --> 00:03:14.660
I just meant it literally.

00:03:14.780 --> 00:03:16.059
I'm saying

00:03:16.060 --> 00:03:19.460
there's something under your throne.

00:03:19.700 --> 00:03:21.239
If you don't blame me

00:03:21.240 --> 00:03:24.180
for what happened
at the Imperial Academy,

00:03:24.780 --> 00:03:27.700
then I'm willing
to split it fifty-fifty with you.

00:03:29.060 --> 00:03:31.340
Now you're bargaining with me too?

00:03:31.860 --> 00:03:33.900
Fine, I agree.

00:03:34.340 --> 00:03:35.739
I'd like to see

00:03:35.740 --> 00:03:39.700
what exactly
is hidden beneath my throne.

00:03:51.780 --> 00:03:52.900
This is...

00:03:56.860 --> 00:03:59.340
Hey, what's going on?

00:04:04.780 --> 00:04:06.739
Well, Grandfather?

00:04:06.740 --> 00:04:10.420
The treasure
under your seat isn't bad, right?

00:04:11.140 --> 00:04:12.360
What exactly happened here?

00:04:12.360 --> 00:04:15.080
At the end of the previous dynasty,
when war and chaos filled the land,

00:04:15.080 --> 00:04:18.179
someone hid treasures
beneath this throne,

00:04:18.180 --> 00:04:21.139
planning to come back for them
after the dynasty changed.

00:04:21.140 --> 00:04:24.139
But no one lived to see that day,

00:04:24.140 --> 00:04:26.260
so these little ones
ended up benefiting from it.

00:04:30.700 --> 00:04:34.219
Isn't this the jade ruyi, the national
treasure of the former dynasty?

00:04:34.220 --> 00:04:35.640
With all these treasures presented to me...

00:04:35.640 --> 00:04:36.899
Grandfather,

00:04:36.900 --> 00:04:38.740
you still haven't agreed to my request.

00:04:39.660 --> 00:04:40.620
Suisui.

00:04:40.780 --> 00:04:42.299
I agree to everything.

00:04:42.300 --> 00:04:43.580
I agree.

00:04:43.660 --> 00:04:44.939
Prince Jing was right.

00:04:44.940 --> 00:04:46.700
You truly are my little lucky star.

00:04:47.260 --> 00:04:50.400
From now on, whoever dares slander you again,
I will be the first to deal with them.

00:05:03.060 --> 00:05:04.900
Deeply regret it?

00:05:06.100 --> 00:05:09.419
My mother just won't give up.

00:05:09.420 --> 00:05:12.420
Now she's even resorted
to hurting herself for sympathy.

00:05:19.440 --> 00:05:22.759
♪Little lucky star,
twinkling with a wink at me♪

00:05:22.760 --> 00:05:26.599
♪Every Chinese New Year day brings
the luckiest fortune slip♪

00:05:26.600 --> 00:05:30.119
♪The God of Wealth favors me,
the Matchmaker ties red strings for me♪

00:05:30.120 --> 00:05:33.080
♪With firecrackers going off,
good things keep coming one after another♪

00:05:33.960 --> 00:05:37.599
♪Make a wish on the very first day
of the Chinese New Year♪

00:05:37.600 --> 00:05:41.360
♪By the second day,
my belly's already round♪

00:05:41.440 --> 00:05:44.759
♪Always talking about dieting,
but the chub never disappears♪

00:05:44.760 --> 00:05:48.800
♪Good food brings joy
and happiness every single day♪

00:05:54.400 --> 00:05:58.079
♪With lucky stars shining bright,
every year is filled with joy♪

00:05:58.080 --> 00:06:01.719
♪I'm bringing blessings to everyone♪

00:06:01.720 --> 00:06:05.439
♪Hands clasped together in greeting♪

00:06:05.440 --> 00:06:09.079
♪May every family be sweet and happy♪

00:06:09.080 --> 00:06:12.759
♪With lucky stars shining bright,
may everything go your way♪

00:06:12.760 --> 00:06:14.679
♪Endlessly flowing♪

00:06:14.680 --> 00:06:20.880
♪Good fortune♪